  "texts": [
    "The focus is on utilizing GAs and RL to investigate whether we can improve the prediction of task durations in complex robotic applications.A distinctive feature of this research is the integration of diversity as a factor within the GA and RL.",
    "By incorporating diversity and allocating a portion of each generation to random selections, we aim to explore a wider range of potential solutions.",
    "In addition, in our RL algorithm we included diversity in our reward function.",
    "This method is intended to mitigate the risks of premature convergence and enhance the robustness of the solution space exploration.",
    "Additionally, we compare these advanced methods to a simpler method using a random algorithm as our baseline to evaluate their effectiveness."
  ],
